==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Midday
<hw>Mid"day`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>middaeg</ets>. See <er>Mid</er>, <pos>a.</pos>, and
<er>Day</er>.]</ety> <def>The middle part of the day; noon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Midday</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Midday
<hw>Mid"day`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to noon;
meridional; <as>as, the <ex>midday</ex> sun</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Midden</ent>⟦br⟧
